<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">شريح قال:</span> الأب <span class="c2">(أحق)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span>، و <span class="c2">(الأم)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> أرفق.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
